sentence: What time do EECS 492 lectures start next semester ?
sentence-with-vars: What time do department0 number0 lectures start next semester ?
sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 492 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = number0 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
